data.description: WELCOME HOME to this beautifully maintained 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home in the highly desired community of Cypress Creek! This split floor plan is perfect for any family with your spacious primary suite in the back of the home and the other two bedrooms up front... This home has been recently updated with all new flooring and a relaxing walk in tub in your primary bathroom... You will enjoy having your morning coffee or your night time cordial on your new entended beautifully paved and screened in back patio area! Benefit from having solar panels and not worrying about high electric bills!!! Cypress Creek is a community with a clubhouse, pools, cabana, basketball courts, dog parks, fitness center and playgrounds. Your low HOA dues include CABLE AND HIGH-SPEED INTERNET!!!! It is also conveniently located near I-75, U.S HWY 301 and 41, near hospitals, major shopping centers, minutes away from the beach, dining, entertainment and more!
